@startuml
[*] --> Initial

Initial --> Assigned_to_Client : Assign to Client
Initial --> Assigned_to_Campaign : Assign to Campaign

Assigned_to_Client --> Unassigned : Remove Assignment
Assigned_to_Client --> Assigned_to_Campaign : Switch Assignment

Assigned_to_Campaign --> Unassigned : Remove Assignment
Assigned_to_Campaign --> Assigned_to_Client : Switch Assignment

Unassigned --> Assigned_to_Client : Assign to Client
Unassigned --> Assigned_to_Campaign : Assign to Campaign
Unassigned --> Unemployed : Leave Job

Unemployed --> Archived : [*]::30days
Archived --> [*]
@enduml
